overview: The Ultimate Top is a Chris Steele gay XXX parody of the hit TV Show The Ultimate Fighter. Starring Kris Jamieson and nine other stacked guys who sign up to become The Ultimate Top, the fighters are split into two teams lead by coaches. Coach Tristan Baldwin takes on the Red Team while Coach Nick Ryder takes on the Blue Team. Which of the eight men have what it takes to become The Ultimate Top?
title: The Ultimate Top
